<br>
Obviously you're going to use piercers mainhand 99% of the time, but getting a good offhander thats a piercer isn't always easy/cheap, because good offhand piercers are often good mainhands as well, and the price reflects this. <br>
<br>
I've been using 1hs offhand since about 47, when I picked up a sword breaker on a VSR killing. That switched to velium swiftblade, then after epic small dragonbone shard for a bit, then blade of the green dragon eye, and currently emerald scimi.<br>
<br>
So, in general, I'd recommend keeping all your skills up, but if you wanted to pick one, I'd go with 1hs.<br>
<br>
Other popular rogue 1hs'ers: centi longsword, crystalline short sword, longsword of ethereal energy, and of the various velium swords from DN etc.<br>
<br>
