had 75 slash last thursday... sold off my second piercing weapon and was stuck with a centilong.  Group screwed yadda yadda yadda i needed barbed ringmail.  Anyway since then its 202 as of today.<br>
<br>
point:<br>
Both parties are right.  one guy was saying dont bother use what ya got.  You wont be at your peek for a half week out of a year of playing time so what.  The other guy was from the point of view that you wouldnt offhand it in a deticated manner.  That you would bow out of exping and raiding to go raise slash and it would take ya 6 hours.  But screw that.  Offhanding a slash doesnt hurt your damage out put that much as a rogue even when its at a 100.  maybe a 20% decrease prior to level 55 even less after.  And it steadily gets better from there.<br>
